amz1 = pd.read_csv("AMZ_level1.csv")
amz1 = amz1.set_index(["Unnamed: 0"])
amz1 = amz1.drop('accuracy')
amz2 = pd.read_csv("AMZ_level2.csv")
amz2 = amz2.set_index(["Unnamed: 0"])
amz2 = amz2.drop('accuracy')
amz3 = pd.read_csv("AMZ_level3.csv")
amz3 = amz3.set_index(["level 3"])
amz3 = amz3.drop('accuracy')
amz4 = pd.read_csv("AMZ_level4.csv")
amz4 = amz4.set_index(["Unnamed: 0"])
amz4 = amz4.drop('accuracy')
amz5 = pd.read_csv("AMZ_level5.csv")
amz5 = amz5.set_index(["Unnamed: 0"])
amz5 = amz5.drop('accuracy')
amz6 = pd.read_csv("AMZ_level6.csv")
amz6 = amz6.set_index(["Unnamed: 0"])
amz6 = amz6.drop('accuracy')

amz_ASWtfidf = list()
amz_ASWtfidf_ngram = list()
amz_ASWw2v = list()
amz_ASWglove = list()
datas = [amz1, amz2, amz3, amz4, amz5, amz6]
for x in datas:
    amz_ASWtfidf.append(x.mean_tfidf['ASW'])
    amz_ASWtfidf_ngram.append(x.mean_tfidf_ngram['ASW'])
    amz_ASWw2v.append(x.mean_w2v['ASW'])
    amz_ASWglove.append(x.mean_glove['ASW'])

y1 = amz_ASWtfidf
y2 = amz_ASWtfidf_ngram
y3 = amz_ASWw2v
y4 = amz_ASWglove

plt.subplot(4, 1, 1)
plt.plot(y1)
plt.title('Amazon ASW')
plt.ylabel('tfidf')
plt.subplot(4, 1, 2)
plt.plot(y2)
plt.ylabel('tfidf ngram')
plt.subplot(4, 1, 3)
plt.plot(y3)
plt.ylabel('w2v')
plt.subplot(4, 1, 4)
plt.plot(y4)
plt.ylabel('GloVe')
plt.xlabel('levels')

plt.show()

# plot all ASW
#tfidf

amzASWtfidf = list()
yelpASWtfidf= list()
dbpediaASWtfidf = list()
amzs = [amz1, amz2, amz3, amz4, amz5, amz6]
dbps = [dbpedia1, dbpedia2, dbpedia3, dbpedia4, dbpedia5, dbpedia6]
yelps = [yelp1, yelp2, yelp3, yelp4, yelp5, yelp6]
for x in amzs:
    amzASWtfidf.append(x.mean_tfidf['ASW'])
for x in dbps:
    dbpediaASWtfidf.append(x.mean_tfidf['ASW'])
for x in yelps:
    yelpASWtfidf.append(x.mean_tfidf['ASW'])

y1 = amzASWtfidf
y2 = yelpASWtfidf
y3 = dbpediaASWtfidf

plt.subplot(3, 1, 1)
plt.plot(y1)
plt.ylabel('Amazon')
plt.title('TFIDF ASW')
plt.subplot(3, 1, 2)
plt.plot(y2)
plt.ylabel('Yelp')
plt.subplot(3, 1, 3)
plt.plot(y3)
plt.ylabel('DBPedia')
plt.xlabel('levels')

plt.show()

amzASWtfidf = list()
yelpASWtfidf= list()
dbpediaASWtfidf = list()
amzs = [amz1, amz2, amz3, amz4, amz5, amz6]
dbps = [dbpedia1, dbpedia2, dbpedia3, dbpedia4, dbpedia5, dbpedia6]
